ol.li:
Check the job status of the CSU file using the steps above. If the status is 0 or 1, change it to 3.
Using the example output in the previous step, if you wanted to change the status of the stalled job you would use this command: update jobs set status=3 where id="80d6c298-8d6f-11e5-a4e3-525400505207";
To cleanup a catalog item, the following sql command will delete all records related to a catalogId: delete from jobs where catalogId="wscatalog.2145";
To cleanup the Sherpa database, the following sql command will drop the jobs table and delete everything in the table: drop table jobs;
